articles.title: Pharrell & His $1 Million Louis Vuitton Bag Are Taking Over Paris - Highsnobiety
articles.description: Pharrell's $1 million crocodile leather Louis Vuitton Speedy handbag is everywhere, as Pharrell takes his bag to sit front row at Paris Fashion Week.
articles.content: Pharrell really is everywhere. Just as we predicted, the reigning Louis Vuitton artistic director, still riding high from his runway debut, has become omnipresent at Paris Fashion Week Spring/Summer … [+3378 chars]
